data.value: We are a group of aspiring programmers that want to add to the experience of Minecraft. This is not for money, or clout, we just want to learn about something new! We are all teenagers, just playing around to see what we can make! Our team is made up of 4 people, DeathlyBower959, YYP, Expando and Jams. If you would like, check our socials on our website!
